    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060700/extras/de6c02a1936ad4ea0bd6522fd82797d3.avif?t=1747033481\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>《重返战场》是一款次世代FPS（第一人称射击）微端游戏，拥有媲美客户端游戏的画面品质、细腻的操作手感和丰富的系统玩法。后续的研发会对美术有更高的要求。官方交流Q群688933547<br>模式介绍<br>团队竞技:以消灭敌人为目标的游戏模式，固定时间内率先消灭规定数量的敌人即可获胜。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060700/extras/dfa896f5947078734a53d101416a63f6.poster.avif?t=1747033481\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060700/extras/dfa896f5947078734a53d101416a63f6.webm?t=1747033481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060700/extras/dfa896f5947078734a53d101416a63f6.mp4?t=1747033481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>爆破模式:进攻方需要使用C4炸弹摧毁目标物，而防守方则要阻止目标物被摧毁，对玩家的配合要求很高，竞技性强。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060700/extras/5c2d462be3d455b20c7ae4554007ee44.poster.avif?t=1747033481\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060700/extras/5c2d462be3d455b20c7ae4554007ee44.webm?t=1747033481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060700/extras/5c2d462be3d455b20c7ae4554007ee44.mp4?t=1747033481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>挑战模式:玩家需要击杀电脑控制的怪物以及最终的关底BOSS，该模式下可以通过杀怪得分来获得最后的奖励箱以及独一无二的BOSS奖励。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060700/extras/5f9f856ee899b41191c7977bc5017605.poster.avif?t=1747033481\" widt